headline: Booking Holdings Inc. to Present at the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference
summary: Booking Holdings (NASDAQ: BKNG) today announced that Chief Financial Officer Ewout Steenbergen will participate in a fireside chat at the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference, held in San Francisco, on September 11, beginning at 10:10 am PT / 1:10 pm ET. A live audio cast of the presentation will be available to the public at https://ir.bookingholdings.com/events, and a replay will be available approximately 24 hours later.

headline: Thrills and Chills: Agoda's Guide to Asia's Lesser-Known Theme Parks Worth Visiting

These parks offer a whirlwind of unique attractions, cultural heritage, and immersive experiences, ensuring an adventure that will have travelers spinning with excitement.
